divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside my house looking at the finale of the lunar eclipse. To the lower right (south east) I saw what I thought was an UFO. At first I thought it was an airplane in a holding pattern because I am about 20 miles from the airport. But the flashing lights are what I found odd. The lights were outlined and flashed back and forth. After a couple minutes it just disappeared sideways.
Summary: Object seemed to hover. Lights were flashing in a row, back and forth
